  - 306
By: Philo
---
In relating the things of the earth to the celestial, and those of heaven to
the inferior, the Chaldeans have shown in the mutual affections between these
parts of the universe (which are separated in space but not in essence) the
harmony that unites them in a sort of musical accord.
